title: Baroque and Rococo (Art Ebook)
description:
Baroque and Rococo
G. P. Putnam's Sons | 1967 | ISBN: 0399100717 | English | 344 pages | PDF | 60.8 MB


This magnificently illustrated volume, written with verve, insight, and remarkable perceptiveness, is one of those rare works of art history that conveys in masterly prose the intimate relationship that exists between an art style, the special conditions that prevailed during the time in which it flourished and which led to its evolution, and the place of its origin
